     <td align="center" width="120" bgcolor="#dddddd"><font class="GraphicCaption">"Gnome and Halfling hybrids?  Ok.  But when do I get to be a monk?"</font></td>
     <td bgcolor="#ffffff"><img src="images/spacer.gif"></td>
